           <h3>
            <a href="https://hr.appstate.edu/hr-services/workers-compensation/initial-notification-injury-form">
             <strong>
              Initial Notification of Incident/Injury Form
             </strong>
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p>
            <a href="https://hr.appstate.edu/hr-services/workers-compensation-and-leave-management/initial-notification-injury-form">
             Click here
            </a>
            to complete a short questionnaire used to notify ASU Human Resource Services and Environmental Health, Safety, &amp; Emergency Management personnel about an on-the-job incident or injury, including near misses.
            <br/>
