           <div>
            <h3>
             <strong>
              Safety and Health Concern Form
             </strong>
            </h3>
            <p>
             <strong>
              Be a Hazard Hero! -
             </strong>
             <strong>
              Help identify and minimize hazards.
             </strong>
            </p>
            <p>
             <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/17LZlHdfhsiG9dK_veOxK1-jJTHukGCeOapTZMMIMg-s/viewform?usp=send_form">
              <strong>
               <img alt="Hazard Hero" class="thumbright" height="188" src="/sites/appsafety.appstate.edu/files/Hazard-Hero-sm.jpg" width="150"/>
              </strong>
             </a>
             As part of North Carolina’s Injury Prevention Hazard Recognition Program, we want all Appalachian faculty, staff, and students to identify and report safety hazards in the workplace and around campus, wherever they are found.  As a Hazard Hero, finding and reporting unsafe conditions and other hazards will help keep our campus safe.
            </p>
            <p>
             Be a Hazard Hero.
             <strong>
              <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/17LZlHdfhsiG9dK_veOxK1-jJTHukGCeOapTZMMIMg-s/viewform?usp=send_form">
               Click here
              </a>
              to report a hazard.
             </strong>
            </p>
            <p>
             This program is designed to assist you in reporting safety concerns and hazards.  Simply complete the short form above and click the SUBMIT button at the bottom of the form.  Your report will go directly to EHS&amp;EM personnel for review and follow-up.  If you have questions, please feel free to contact our office by email (
             <a href="mailto:safety@appstate.edu">
              safety@appstate.edu
             </a>
             ) or by phone at 828-262-4008.
            </p>
            <p>
             <strong>
              <strong>
               <strong>
                <strong>
                 --------------------------------------------------------------------
                </strong>
               </strong>
              </strong>
             </strong>
            </p>
            <p>
             <strong>
              Hazardous Chemical Information Now Online
             </strong>
            </p>
            <p>
             <a href="https://msdsmanagement.msdsonline.com/e092436a-a13e-463c-b499-ee43bdc65d48/ebinder/?nas=True%20">
              Click here
             </a>
             to find an MSDS (now called SDS or Safety Data Sheets).
            </p>
            <p>
             <a href="https://chematixprod.its.appstate.edu/Chematix/">
              Click here
             </a>
             to log into the ASU Chematix™ hazardous chemical tracking system.
             <br/>
             (Contact EHS&amp;EM for initial log in.)
            </p>
